          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: spotty support and factual inaccuracies on niche topics</h4><p>Multi-language content is harder to quality-check, and the support team can't cover every language's nuances well.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

