      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#9 · $499-2,499/MO · FULL-SERVICE</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Adaptify — Best full-service alternative to a traditional agency</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For businesses with $500+/month budgets that want strategy + content + backlinks without hiring a full team.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Adaptify is the closest thing to replacing an actual SEO agency on this list — weekly strategy updates, long-form E-E-A-T articles, journalist PR backlink outreach, and reporting. At $499/month minimum, it's 5x the cost of most competitors. Still 50-90% cheaper than mid-tier agencies charging $3,000+, though. No schema markup support and limited to four CMS platforms are real gaps.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Most complete: strategy + content + backlinks + reporting</h4><p>The only option on this list that bundles journalist-relationship backlinks with weekly strategy updates.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Backlinks via real journalist relationships — not link exchange</h4><p>Earned links through PR outreach carry far less algorithmic risk than exchange networks.</p></div></li>
