          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: $499 minimum is 5x competitors — and no schema support</h4><p>No schema markup and WordPress/Shopify/Wix/Webflow only. Hard to justify at 5x when theStacc delivers 30 articles at $99.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

