        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Scalenut's Cruise Mode produces 1,500+ word articles in ~5 minutes — impressive speed, but each piece needs 20-60% editing before publishing. That makes it an assisted writing tool, not a done-for-you tool. NLP-powered topic research and content optimization scoring are genuinely useful for teams that already have editors. Keyword stuffing issues and robotic phrasing are recurring complaints.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Fast article production — 1,500 words in ~5 minutes</h4><p>Massive time saving for writers who already know how to edit AI output.</p></div></li>
