          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: 2.5/5 Trustpilot, disappearing credits, heavy editing needed</h4><p>This is a first-draft generator, not a publisher. Plan for significant editorial investment.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
