        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What does "done-for-you SEO" actually mean?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">The tool manages keyword research, writing, optimization, and publishing without manual input following initial configuration. Automation depth varies — some tools are fully hands-off (theStacc, Emplibot, RankYak); others produce drafts needing significant revision (Scalenut, RightBlogger).</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can automated SEO content actually rank on Google?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Ahrefs research shows AI-generated content appears in a significant percentage of top-10 Google results. Quality and relevance matter — thin, keyword-stuffed content won't rank. Tools with NLP optimization and topical depth perform best.</div>
        </div>
